      "contentPreview": "# User Profile\n\nDisplays user info...",
      "content": null,
      "markdownContent": "# User Profile\n\n## Overview\nDisplays user information and settings. Accessible after login via the [[Auth Screen]].\n\n## Features\n- Avatar upload\n- Display name editing\n- Notification preferences\n- Account deletion"
    },
